parameters:
The rumored irreversible groping group was a
complete disappointment.

Of course, there is also information connecting to
the Pink Snake gang.

Due to the time it took to hand over the groper,
we couldn't go around and check all the
vehicles...

Kenichi (Well, I guess it's good that he
contributed to the town's public safety, even if
it's just a little bit)
When Rurika and I returned to the meeting place...

Rurika: It seems like they have achieved some
results over there.

Sakura: Hey, you're late. These guys are the
infamous groping group, and I caught all of them.

Kimohiko: Good work, Onee-chan Rurika and Kenichi-
kun.

Kimohiko: Ehehe, it's amazing, right? We caught
these guys, me and Onee-chan Sakura♪
Kenichi: Ah, ah... This is really amazing.

To catch nearly ten gropers with just two
people...

Sakura, Onee-san... You must have done something
quite reckless, huh...
Well, on the contrary...

Kenichi: They're all beaten up. Even though
they're gropers, isn't this going a bit too far?

Kenichi: Ah, could it be because they have
connections with the Pink Snake Gang?

Kimohiko: Eh, no. Those guys are just people with
a hobby of liking groping.
Kenichi: Isn't this going too far!?

Sakura: It's fine. I'll treat those perverts so
badly that they won't even be able to speak.
Middle-aged man: U-U-Uu... I-I-I lost...

Middle-aged man: To go that far just to catch
us...

Middle-aged man: Even if I get caught, I have no
regrets.

Middle-aged man: I will quietly accept my
punishment and atone for my sins...
Middle-aged man: Ughh!!

Sakura: The perpetrators of the group molestation
shouldn't act all cool.

As expected of Onee-san Sakura, she shows no
mercy.
Well, but if it's this...

There's no way someone as creepy as Kimohiko could
be a groper, right?
I might feel a little relieved.
Kimohiko: Ah, that's right.

Kimohiko: Speaking of groping, it reminded me that
there's a hidden warehouse of the Pink Snake gang
around here♪

Kimohiko: I'm sure there's something useful
inside.

Sakura: ...is that so? Let's collect it later,
just in case.

Rurika: ...Yes, let's make sure to collect it
without forgetting.
Kenichi: ......?

Kenichi and the others conducted an undercover
investigation on a crowded train.

Based on the information from SYSTEM Kimohiko,
they exposed the hidden warehouse of the Pink
Snake gang.
Obtained a contribution of \C[4]500P\C[0]!

SYSTEM\I[306]\C[4]Obtained Special Chip
Alpha\C[0]!

SYSTEM\I[305]\C[4]Obtained Low-grade Mithril
Ore\C[0]!

The hidden event '\I[84]\C[4]Groping Train
01\C[0]' has been unlocked.
Rurika: S-Sorry to keep you waiting.
Kimohiko: Ehehe, I'm home~♪
Kenichi: Welcome back, Onee-san Rurika.

Kenichi (What's up with Kimohiko... He seems oddly
cheerful... He's such a weirdo)

Rurika: To cut to the chase, we couldn't confirm
the existence of the Pink Snake gang in
particular.

Rurika: However, it seems that they are indeed
being used to gather discreetly and avoid
attracting attention.

Rurika: This time, there was a gathering of sorts
with a slightly unusual hobby.
Kenichi: Is that so...

Kenichi: Well then, I guess the investigation is
over now?
Rurika: ...That is...

Kimohiko: Um, well, this investigation is over for
now. But in the future, I'll continue to conduct
regular investigations from time to time♪
Kenichi: Huh?

Kimohiko: Onee-chan, didn't you say that they're
being used for gatherings to avoid attracting
attention?

Kimohiko: So, we should keep an eye on it in the
future.
Kimohiko: That's right, Onee-chan Rurika.
Rurika: ...Yes, that's right.
Kenichi: ......?

Kenichi: Well, if it's Onee-chan Rurika's
judgment...?
Sakura: ...I see, so is that all?

Kimohiko: Um, well, it's unrelated to the
investigation but...

Kimohiko: There's a hidden warehouse of the Pink
Snake gang nearby♪
Kimohiko: No, I actually remembered something♪

Kimohiko: I'm sure there's something useful
inside.
Sakura: Alright, I'll collect it later.
Kenichi: ...?
It felt a little strange somehow.

The undercover investigation at the beach ended
just like that.

Kenichi and the others conducted an undercover
investigation at the beach.

Based on Kimohiko's information, they raided the
Pink Snake gang's hidden warehouse.
